我回头再打过去
I'll call her back.

349
00:25:56,390 --> 00:25:58,800
稍等  密查姆
Hang on, boys. Meechum?

350
00:25:58,900 --> 00:26:00,290
还在这儿  先生
It's here, sir.

351
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:01,640
你都了解到了什么
What can you tell me?

352
00:26:01,790 --> 00:26:04,830
昨天  一个叫莱斯利·麦金泰尔的女人
Yesterday, a woman named Leslie McIntyre

353
00:26:04,830 --> 00:26:05,860
开了个新保险箱
opened a new box.

354
00:26:05,860 --> 00:26:06,850
我正在查这个名字
I'm having the name run now,

355
00:26:06,850 --> 00:26:08,660
但她似乎用了假社保号
but it looks like she used a fake social.

356
00:26:08,660 --> 00:26:10,200
监控录像呢
What about security footage?

357
00:26:10,200 --> 00:26:11,810
他们每天早上重置摄像头
They reset the cameras every morning.

358
00:26:11,810 --> 00:26:12,840
我问了她长什么样
I asked what she looked like

359
00:26:12,840 --> 00:26:15,520
经理只说是个白人黑发女人
and all the manager said is that it was a Caucasian brunette.

360
00:26:15,520 --> 00:26:16,700
没什么异常之处
Nothing strange about her.

361
00:26:16,700 --> 00:26:18,520
好吧  把盒子拿回来
All right. Bring the box back here.

362
00:26:18,520 --> 00:26:20,140
一刻别让它离开你的视线范围
Don't let it out of your sight.

363
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:25,610
就我所知  只有一张照片
As far as I know, there's only one photograph.

364
00:26:25,610 --> 00:26:27,440
密查姆说照片还在银行
Meechum says it's still at the bank.

365
00:26:30,410 --> 00:26:31,590
先生  是我一个人了
Sir, it's just me.

366
00:26:33,590 --> 00:26:35,330
你跟我想到一起了吗
Are you thinking what I'm thinking?

367
00:26:35,770 --> 00:26:36,800
是的  先生
Yes, sir.

368
00:26:37,390 --> 00:26:39,010
你盯住他
Well, you keep an eye on him.

369
00:26:44,140 --> 00:26:46,860
我要白宫所有人的邮件和电话记录
I want emails and phone records of everyone in the White House.

370
00:26:47,300 --> 00:26:48,450
包括你的
Including yours.

371
00:26:49,350 --> 00:26:51,360
我的  你真觉得...
Mine? You honestly think--

372
00:26:51,360 --> 00:26:52,530
有什么问题吗
Is there a problem?

373
00:26:53,510 --> 00:26:54,400
没有
No.

374
00:26:56,390 --> 00:26:57,300
很好
Good.

375
00:27:03,080 --> 00:27:04,130
真是不幸
It's unfortunate.

376
00:27:04,130 --> 00:27:06,500
邓巴女士  邓巴女士
Ms. Dunbar! Ms. Dunbar? Ms. Dunbar?

377
00:27:06,510 --> 00:27:07,520
这样的画面
The imagery...

378
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:09,810
居然有人靠如此卑劣的手段
That anyone would try to inflame racial discord

379
00:27:09,820 --> 00:27:11,810
企图煽动种族不和
by doing something so base.

380
00:27:11,950 --> 00:27:14,350
那是不是凯文·安德伍德根本不重要
Whether it's Calvin Underwood isn't the point.

381
00:27:14,350 --> 00:27:17,160
即便是  这一点我们无法确认
If it is, and we have no confirmation on that,

382
00:27:17,160 --> 00:27:20,030
那么是谁挂上去的  为什么要这么做
I mean... Who put this up? And why?

383
00:27:20,190 --> 00:27:21,390
谁知道呢
Who knows.

384
00:27:21,390 --> 00:27:24,590
而且父亲的罪未必是孩子的罪
And the sins of the father aren't necessarily the sins of the son.

385
00:27:24,590 --> 00:27:27,950
但  这令人不安  十分不安
But... it's troubling. Very troubling.

386
00:27:28,830 --> 00:27:32,130
这样的伎俩很可能揭开旧疮疤
Stunts like these have the potential to open old wounds.

387
00:27:32,130 --> 00:27:35,430
我们不能允许那样的事发生  我们得不受其影响
We can't let that happen. We need to rise above it.

388
00:27:35,430 --> 00:27:38,240
要明白  不管你支持谁
Make clear, no matter who you support,

389
00:27:38,240 --> 00:27:40,970
这样的行为是不可容忍的
that this sort of behavior will not be tolerated.

390
00:27:40,970 --> 00:27:43,950
给我接克拉克牧师和吉恩·克兰希
Get me Reverend Clark and Gene Clancy on the phone.

391
00:28:04,890 --> 00:28:07,150
他们要你去大巴那边
Hey, they want you out by the bus.

392
00:28:07,490 --> 00:28:08,480
大巴那边
By the bus?

393
00:28:08,480 --> 00:28:10,330
-你是谁  -抱歉
- Um, who are you? - Sorry.

394
00:28:10,330 --> 00:28:11,970
巴特勒县办公室的马克
Mark from the Butler County office.

395
00:28:11,970 --> 00:28:13,330
他们要辛辛那提的志愿者
They want all the Cincinnati volunteers

396
00:28:13,330 --> 00:28:15,240
都去大巴那边集合跟邓巴合影
to gather by the bus for a photo with Dunbar.

397
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:16,700
珍告诉我我不能离开岗位的
Jenn told me I wasn't supposed to leave--

398
00:28:16,700 --> 00:28:17,930
所以她叫我过来喊你
That's why she sent me.

399
00:28:17,930 --> 00:28:19,660
她不希望你错过合影  去吧
She didn't want you to miss the photo. Go.

400
00:28:19,670 --> 00:28:21,000
大巴那边吗
Out by the bus?

401
00:28:21,250 --> 00:28:22,570
她叫我替你
She told me to cover for you.

402
00:28:23,590 --> 00:28:24,950
好
Okay, um...

403
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:26,900
有几个人没来
well, there were a couple of no-shows,

404
00:28:26,900 --> 00:28:28,410
其他人都来了
but, you know, otherwise, everyone's here.

405
00:28:28,410 --> 00:28:30,720
-好  谢谢  -太棒了  谢谢
- Okay. Thanks. - Very convenient. Thanks.

406
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:31,640
快去吧
Enjoy.

407
00:29:08,940 --> 00:29:11,160
我是《克利夫兰老实人报》的戴维·格里姆斯
I'm David Grimes with the Cleveland Plain Dealer.

408
00:29:12,090 --> 00:29:13,150
你的证件呢
Where's your credential?

409
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:15,790
我蠢得把证件忘在车里了
I was an idiot and left it in the car.

410
00:29:15,790 --> 00:29:18,880
不过前台签到处的人认识我
They recognized me at the check-in desk, though.

411
00:29:19,540 --> 00:29:20,660
我可以带你去等候处
I can direct you to the bullpen,

412
00:29:20,660 --> 00:29:22,070
但是这一区不对媒体开放
but this area is off-limits to the press.

413
00:29:22,080 --> 00:29:24,270
我其实是来采访辛西娅·德里斯科尔的
I'm actually supposed to do an interview with Cynthia Driscoll.

414
00:29:24,270 --> 00:29:26,360
先遣人员叫我来这边
The Advance guys said I should come this way.

415
00:29:28,140 --> 00:29:29,030
在这里等一下
Wait here.

416
00:29:38,840 --> 00:29:42,110
抱歉  总统先生  我们做不到
I'm sorry, Mr. President, we just can't do it.

417
00:29:42,110 --> 00:29:44,910
这里45%的选票在非裔手中
Forty-five percent of the vote here is African American.

418
00:29:44,910 --> 00:29:47,210
你和你母亲对我的支持
You and your mother standing by my side

419
00:29:47,210 --> 00:29:48,380
会有很重要的作用...
would go a long way to put this--

420
00:29:48,380 --> 00:29:51,960
我在一个非裔及拉丁裔的选区竞选议员
I am running for Congress in a black and Latino district.

421
00:29:52,170 --> 00:29:55,800
我母亲曾在游行时被暴打  被水冲
My mother was beaten and hosed down in marches.

422
00:29:55,800 --> 00:29:59,220
你想让我们替一个三K党人的儿子作担保吗
You want us to vouch for a man whose father was in the KKK?

423
00:29:59,230 --> 00:30:02,360
-不  他不是三K党  -照片上那个就是他
- No, he was not in the Klan. - That was him in that picture.

424
00:30:02,360 --> 00:30:03,780
对  可这个我已经解释过了
Yes, but I've explained that.

425
00:30:03,780 --> 00:30:05,840
内战就是在本州掀起的
This is the state where the Civil War started,

426
00:30:05,840 --> 00:30:08,100
有些人汽车保险杠上还贴着南军旗贴纸
where you can still see rebel flags on bumper stickers.

427
00:30:08,100 --> 00:30:12,000
这里曾有很严重的种族暴行  总统先生
There is a history of racist brutality here, Mr. President.

428
00:30:12,610 --> 00:30:14,790
那种符号影响很大
Those sort of symbols matter.

429
00:30:15,380 --> 00:30:17,240
能让你母亲接电话吗
Could you put your mother on, please?

430
00:30:20,490 --> 00:30:21,400
妈妈
Mom?

431
00:30:21,760 --> 00:30:22,890
他想跟你说话
He wants to speak to you.

432
00:30:27,620 --> 00:30:28,750
总统先生
Mr. President.

433
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:32,470
听着  我们需要团结  我为西莉娅背书了
Listen, we need to stand together. Now, I've endorsed Celia.

434
00:30:32,470 --> 00:30:34,910
克莱尔在德州能给她帮很大忙
Claire can do a great deal for her in Texas.

435
00:30:34,950 --> 00:30:38,280
现在远离安德伍德一家对她更好
She's better off without the Underwoods at this point.

436
00:30:38,280 --> 00:30:39,720
那你的诊所呢
But what about your clinic?

437
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:43,070
你要是拿我们的诊所要挟我  别人会怎么看
Imagine how that would look, holding our clinic for ransom.

438
00:30:43,120 --> 00:30:46,220
我是想博取您的好意  议员女士
I'm appealing to your goodwill, Congresswoman.

439
00:30:46,510 --> 00:30:50,080
等我们不再遭受殴打和枪击
When we stop getting beaten and shot...

440
00:30:50,990 --> 00:30:53,530
我会好意待您的  总统先生
you'll have my goodwill, Mr. President.

441
00:30:54,420 --> 00:30:55,390
再见
Goodbye.

442
00:31:02,670 --> 00:31:04,210
再接吉恩·克兰希
Get me Gene Clancy again.

443
00:31:07,080 --> 00:31:09,140
会不会是奥林·蔡斯  弗兰西斯
What if it's Oren Chase, Francis?

444
00:31:09,880 --> 00:31:11,400
他也可能拿到一份副本
He could've gotten his hands on a copy.

445
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:12,780
照片可能不止一张
There may be more than one.

446
00:31:14,350 --> 00:31:16,070
先打给密查姆  然后克兰希
Meechum first, then Clancy.

447
00:31:22,180 --> 00:31:23,190
卢卡斯
Lucas?

448
00:31:24,710 --> 00:31:25,910
我们得谈谈
We need to talk.

449
00:31:26,610 --> 00:31:29,440
-我还以为你...  -是的  不过已经出来了
- I thought you were--  - I was. I'm... I'm out now.

450
00:31:29,870 --> 00:31:31,100
这很重要
This is important.

451
00:31:32,490 --> 00:31:35,140
总统先生  您父亲是种族主义者吗
Mr. President, was your father a racist?

452
00:31:42,260 --> 00:31:44,410
您父亲是种族主义者吗
Was your father a racist?

453
00:31:47,850 --> 00:31:49,930
安德伍德夫人  你母亲还好吗
Mrs. Underwood, is your mother okay?

454
00:31:52,360 --> 00:31:53,770
总统先生
Mr. President!

455
00:31:58,010 --> 00:31:59,690
-蔡斯先生  -你是谁
- Mr. Chase? - Who are you?

456
00:32:00,010 --> 00:32:01,600
特勤局的
United States Secret Service.

457
00:32:01,980 --> 00:32:03,160
我们要的不是你  蔡斯先生
We're not after you, Mr. Chase.

458
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:04,870
我们是想要指使你这么干的人
We're after whoever put you up to it.

459
00:32:04,870 --> 00:32:05,960
指使我做什么
Put me up to what?

460
00:32:06,470 --> 00:32:07,380
你可以现在回答我
You can answer me here,

461
00:32:07,380 --> 00:32:09,980
或者我们可以去问哥伦比亚办事处
or we can go to the Columbia field office for questioning.

462
00:32:10,050 --> 00:32:11,460
我不知道你在说什么
I have no idea what you're talking about.

463
00:32:11,460 --> 00:32:13,060
请您跟我来一下  先生
All right, I need you to come with me, sir.

464
00:32:13,060 --> 00:32:15,290
-等等  -请出来  先生
- Now, hold on. - Step outside, sir.

465
00:32:16,100 --> 00:32:17,780
我要找律师
I wanna talk to a lawyer.

466
00:32:18,700 --> 00:32:20,730
4126号需要支援
I need backup at 4126.

467
00:32:20,730 --> 00:32:23,440
-没必要这样吧  -除非你合作  先生
- Come on, that's not necessary. - Not if you cooperate, sir.

468
00:32:25,420 --> 00:32:27,810
我告诉你不会惹麻烦吧
If I talk to you, I won't get in trouble?

469
00:32:29,350 --> 00:32:31,690
我向上帝起誓  邓巴女士  这都是真的
I swear to God, Ms. Dunbar. It's all true.

470
00:32:31,690 --> 00:32:32,810
证据呢
Then where's the proof?

471
00:32:32,810 --> 00:32:35,520
我没办法找证据  但你可以
I don't have the means, but you do.

472
00:32:36,170 --> 00:32:38,810
你调查过他  你知道他很危险
You've investigated him before. You know he's dangerous.

473
00:32:38,820 --> 00:32:39,610
古德温先生
Mr. Goodwin--

474
00:32:39,610 --> 00:32:41,850
如果我不是查到了真相  他为什么要针对我
Why would he go after me if I wasn't onto something?

475
00:32:41,850 --> 00:32:44,120
这是一起高级钓鱼执法
This was a high-level sting operation.

476
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:46,170
为此调动了大量资源
Major resources were dedicated to it.

477
00:32:46,170 --> 00:32:48,660
我原本是个记者  没有犯罪记录
I'm... I was a journalist, no criminal record.

478
00:32:48,660 --> 00:32:50,440
怎么突然就成了威胁  除非我...
How am I suddenly such a threat, unless I'm--

479
00:32:50,450 --> 00:32:51,810
就算我相信你
Even if I did believe you,

480
00:32:51,810 --> 00:32:55,520
我已经不是司法部的了  现在只是个普通市民
I am no longer part of the DOJ. I am a private citizen now.

481
00:32:55,520 --> 00:32:56,860
正在竞选总统
Who's running for president--

482
00:32:56,860 --> 00:32:59,260
你来这儿不违反证人保护计划的规定吗
Aren't you breaking WITSEC protocol by being here?

483
00:32:59,270 --> 00:33:00,900
我不想再跟他谈了
I am no longer comfortable with this.

484
00:33:00,900 --> 00:33:02,930
你是我最后的机会  求你了
You're... you're my last chance. Please!

485
00:33:02,930 --> 00:33:05,460
-我建议你还是回家吧  -我  可是我
- I suggest that you go back home. - I'm... The things I've--

486
00:33:05,460 --> 00:33:07,690
-别逼我们叫保安  -求你了  就
- Don't make us get security involved.  - Please. Just--

487
00:33:07,690 --> 00:33:10,180
你得在这儿等五分钟  让她先离开
Just give us five minutes until she's out of the building.

488
00:33:10,180 --> 00:33:12,910
求你了  求你听我说
Please. Please listen to me.

489
00:33:13,260 --> 00:33:14,690
我求你了
I'm... I'm begging you.

490
00:33:15,010 --> 00:33:16,410
帮帮我
Just help me...

491
00:33:17,010 --> 00:33:18,080
帮帮我
Help.

492
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:28,340
求你了  求你了
Please, please...

493
00:33:30,460 --> 00:33:31,760
天呐
Oh, God...

494
00:33:33,340 --> 00:33:35,210
你怎么能让我跟他见面
How could you put me in a room with him?

495
00:33:35,430 --> 00:33:37,090
我并不知道他想要说什么
I didn't know what he was gonna say.

496
00:33:37,090 --> 00:33:38,840
不过我以为他这么煞费苦心
But I assumed that if he went to such great lengths--

497
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:42,100
他只有酒驾的证据  那什么都不算上
The DUI, that's all he has proof of. That's nothing.

498
00:33:42,100 --> 00:33:44,210
我都帮过别人逃脱酒驾的惩罚
Even I have helped people get off for that.

499
00:33:44,210 --> 00:33:46,650
-还有外遇  -没证据
- There's the affair... - With no evidence.

500
00:33:46,650 --> 00:33:49,350
他又扯什么谋杀  还杀了两个
Then he leaps to murder... Two murders?

501
00:33:49,350 --> 00:33:50,830
这人有病
The man is troubled.

502
00:33:51,050 --> 00:33:52,630
他那眼神我们都看见了
We saw the look in his eye.

503
00:33:52,820 --> 00:33:54,670
我以为他有什么真凭实据呢
I thought he might have something real.

504
00:33:55,390 --> 00:33:57,110
他以前做编辑做得挺好的
He used to be a good editor.

505
00:33:57,200 --> 00:33:59,130
可他现在是个定了罪的重犯
And now he is a convicted felon.

506
00:33:59,140 --> 00:34:01,190
你说要想尽一切办法的
You said no stone unturned.

507
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:06,410
对不起  我应该想得更周到一些的
I'm sorry, I should have thought better of it.

508
00:34:06,410 --> 00:34:07,750
是啊  你是应该
Yes, you should have.

509
00:34:10,210 --> 00:34:13,030
就这样吧  我们在南卡罗来纳情况如何
Let's let it go. How are we doing in South Carolina?

510
00:34:13,040 --> 00:34:14,540
早期出口民调结果不错
Early exit polls are good.

511
00:34:14,920 --> 00:34:17,650
-我们有机会赢  -真能赢吗
- We have a shot at winning. - Actually winning?

512
00:34:18,160 --> 00:34:19,920
那个广告牌造成了不小的破坏
That billboard's done real damage.

513
00:34:24,710 --> 00:34:26,230
你能这么做我很感激  吉恩
I appreciate you doing this, Gene.

514
00:34:26,230 --> 00:34:28,020
你真是救了我一命
You're really saving my life here.

515
00:34:28,020 --> 00:34:30,340
等我竞选县长的时候你记着就行
Just remember it when I run for county executive.

516
00:34:30,340 --> 00:34:32,250
你随时需要我随时过来
I'll be down here whenever you need me.

517
00:34:32,250 --> 00:34:35,640
重点不在时间  而是给什么和给多少
Oh, it's not the when, it's the what. And how much.

518
00:34:38,860 --> 00:34:40,470
下午好  奥林
Afternoon, Oren.

519
00:34:40,700 --> 00:34:42,990
-总统先生  -坐吧
- Mr. President. - Have a seat.

520
00:34:47,200 --> 00:34:50,460
上次大桃子的事你还没长记性啊
Didn't you learn your lesson with all that Peachoid nonsense?

521
