694
00:44:54,320 --> 00:44:55,530
我很感激
I appreciate it.

695
00:45:02,700 --> 00:45:06,160
我去外面车队那里了  先生  有事叫我
I'll be out by the motorcade, sir, if you need anything.

696
00:45:06,700 --> 00:45:07,720
谢谢  密查姆
Thank you, Meechum.

697
00:46:12,320 --> 00:46:14,730
我就知道  但是不愿相信
I knew it, but I didn't wanna believe it.

698
00:46:41,200 --> 00:46:42,700
只是个伤口罢了
It's only a wound.

699
00:46:42,780 --> 00:46:43,960
并不致命
It's not fatal.

700
00:46:44,530 --> 00:46:47,060
我的家乡  克莱尔
My home state, Claire.

701
00:46:47,760 --> 00:46:48,730
坐
Have a seat.

702
00:46:48,920 --> 00:46:50,700
我终结了你的竞选  所以你以牙还牙
I end your race so you end mine?

703
00:46:50,700 --> 00:46:53,130
-听我解释  弗兰西斯  -赌气  报复
- Let me explain, Francis. - Spite, revenge!

704
00:46:53,400 --> 00:46:56,040
坐下吧  我们得谈谈
Please, sit down. We need to talk.

705
00:46:58,430 --> 00:47:00,950
现在生气也没用
Nothing is going to come from anger right now.

706
00:47:20,190 --> 00:47:23,700
昨晚聊天的时候  你说这座房子是宫殿
Last night when we were talking, you called this house a palace.

707
00:47:24,810 --> 00:47:26,490
这是我们开始的地方
This is where we began.

708
00:47:27,620 --> 00:47:30,230
你还记得我母亲差点离开了爸爸
And do you remember when my mother almost left Daddy

709
00:47:30,230 --> 00:47:32,530
就因为他资助了你的竞选吗
because he funded your campaign?

710
00:47:32,860 --> 00:47:34,790
她就是那么讨厌你
That's how much she hated you.

711
00:47:35,540 --> 00:47:36,770
但我当时不在意
But I didn't care,

712
00:47:37,090 --> 00:47:39,580
因为我看到了你的潜质  我看到了未来
because I saw something. I saw a future.

713
00:47:39,840 --> 00:47:40,930
我们的未来
Our future.

714
00:47:41,530 --> 00:47:44,800
你开始摧毁一切之前  我们原本还有未来
We had a future until you started destroying it.

715
00:47:44,960 --> 00:47:47,050
要不你不会听的
Well, you wouldn't have listened otherwise.

716
00:47:47,050 --> 00:47:49,010
我一直都听你的
I always listen to you.

717
00:47:49,560 --> 00:47:51,940
只在我说了你想听的的时候
Only when it's what you want to hear.

718
00:47:52,910 --> 00:47:56,640
好吧  克莱尔  我现在在听
Well, all right, Claire. I'm listening now.

719
00:47:56,830 --> 00:47:59,830
你有什么话这么想说
What is it you so desperately needed to say?

720
00:48:00,400 --> 00:48:02,620
三十年来我们从没输过竞选
We've never lost a race in 30 years.

721
00:48:02,620 --> 00:48:05,530
我们从这里开始  所向披靡
We started here and we've always won.

722
00:48:05,530 --> 00:48:06,920
你我一起
You and I, together.

723
00:48:07,840 --> 00:48:09,830
但你要输了  弗兰西斯
But you are losing, Francis.

724
00:48:10,240 --> 00:48:12,610
人们承受不起高价油
People are getting killed at the gas pumps.

725
00:48:13,370 --> 00:48:15,800
《美国就业法案》不及预期
America Works is falling flat.

726
00:48:16,120 --> 00:48:19,920
你的竞选经理看不清现在的形势
Your campaign manager is ten years behind ten years ago.

727
00:48:20,780 --> 00:48:22,570
你没有值得考虑的竞选搭档
You don't have a viable running mate.

728
00:48:22,570 --> 00:48:25,000
我们都清楚不能是唐纳德·布莱斯
We both know it can't be Donald Blythe.

729
00:48:25,140 --> 00:48:26,580
当然不能
Well, of course not.

730
00:48:26,580 --> 00:48:28,620
但我连名都提不上
But I have to win the goddamn nomination

731
00:48:28,620 --> 00:48:29,460
还考虑什么输赢
before I can start worrying about winning.

732
00:48:29,460 --> 00:48:31,090
就算我没这么做
Even if I hadn't done what I did,

733
00:48:31,090 --> 00:48:33,320
你的竞选也问题重重
your race is in real trouble.

734
00:48:34,330 --> 00:48:35,710
你需要我  弗兰西斯
You need me, Francis.

735
00:48:36,760 --> 00:48:39,160
我的支持率比你高
My approvals are higher than yours.

736
00:48:39,160 --> 00:48:40,860
我能帮你赢下德州
I can help you win Texas.

737
00:48:41,010 --> 00:48:44,050
没错  所以我不希望你在达拉斯竞选
Exactly. Which is why I didn't want you running in Dallas.

738
00:48:44,050 --> 00:48:46,110
我需要你在我身旁
I need you at my side.

739
00:48:46,110 --> 00:48:48,270
没错  但是以另一种方式
Yes, but in a different way.

740
00:48:48,590 --> 00:48:49,770
什么方式
Different how?

741
00:48:50,810 --> 00:48:53,370
我们能相互扶持  让彼此更强  对吧
We make each other stronger, can we agree to that?

742
00:48:54,280 --> 00:48:56,980
那得步调协调  但现在不是这样
When it's working, but it's not working.

743
00:48:56,980 --> 00:48:58,500
我们能协调好
We can make it work.

744
00:48:59,700 --> 00:49:04,100
我们能实现当初结婚时我看到的未来
We can accomplish that future I saw when we first got married.

745
00:49:04,640 --> 00:49:08,220
我们作为搭档  真正的搭档
It was us, as partners, real partners.

746
00:49:09,020 --> 00:49:10,940
我们再一起竞选吧
Let's run together, again.

747
00:49:11,380 --> 00:49:13,670
不只作为夫妻
Not just as husband and wife.

748
00:49:21,260 --> 00:49:22,520
你不是指...
You don't mean...

749
00:49:23,140 --> 00:49:24,060
没错
Yes.

750
00:49:27,950 --> 00:49:30,250
我很担心你  克莱尔
I'm worried about you, Claire.

751
00:49:32,310 --> 00:49:35,130
你在说疯话  你被自负蒙蔽了
You're not making any sense. You've let your ego get in the way--

752
00:49:35,130 --> 00:49:37,090
我一直都是你的竞选搭档
I've always been your running mate.

753
00:49:37,090 --> 00:49:39,830
-你只是不愿承认  -当我的副总统吗
- You just didn't wanna see it. - As my vice president?

754
00:49:39,830 --> 00:49:42,380
-天啊  你知道这...  -我反复考虑过了
- Jesus. Do you have any idea--  - I've put a lot of thought into this.

755
00:49:42,390 --> 00:49:43,860
你肯定没想清楚
You can't have thought it through.

756
00:49:43,860 --> 00:49:45,450
-如果你真想透彻了  -她没经验
- Because if you did, you'd come up - She has no experience.

757
00:49:45,450 --> 00:49:46,810
-就能想到千万个理由  -她从没竞选过
- with a million reasons-- - She's never run for anything.

758
00:49:46,810 --> 00:49:50,850
无子  任人唯亲  傲慢  我都考虑过了
No children, nepotism, arrogance, I've run through them all.

759
00:49:52,630 --> 00:49:54,380
没我你赢不了
You can't win without me.

760
00:49:57,070 --> 00:50:00,990
我宁愿选懦弱的唐纳德·布莱斯当我的副总统
I would rather have a spineless Donald Blythe as my vice president

761
00:50:00,990 --> 00:50:04,010
也强过一个没当选过公职的女人
than a woman who's never held elected office.

762
00:50:04,580 --> 00:50:08,070
你要输给一个没当选过公职的女人了
You're losing to a woman who's never held elected office.

763
00:50:09,570 --> 00:50:11,680
你不配
You don't deserve it.

764
00:50:11,950 --> 00:50:16,280
你没尝过一无所有的滋味
You have no idea what it means to have nothing.

765
00:50:16,280 --> 00:50:19,760
你不重视我们的成就
You don't value what we have achieved.

766
00:50:20,670 --> 00:50:24,760
我这辈子事事都要靠自己努力争取
I have had to fight for everything my entire life.

767
00:50:29,600 --> 00:50:31,380
你知道我为什么留着这张照片吗
Do you know why I kept this?

768
00:50:32,020 --> 00:50:33,090
你知道吗
Do you know?

769
00:50:33,620 --> 00:50:37,650
因为这是我唯一一次为我父亲骄傲
Because it's the one time I was proud of my father.

770
00:50:38,020 --> 00:50:42,370
因为这个男人在这一刻  虽然可鄙
Because this man, in this moment, as despicable as it was,

771
00:50:42,370 --> 00:50:44,630
在为生存而奋斗
is fighting to survive.

772
00:50:45,250 --> 00:50:48,320
他不惜一切
He is doing whatever it took.

773
00:50:49,030 --> 00:50:51,620
有没有你  我也会这样
And so will I, with or without you.

774
00:50:51,620 --> 00:50:54,460
所以我不要跟你谈下去了
So no, I will not have this conversation.

775
00:50:54,460 --> 00:50:56,250
我不会再纵容你了
I will not indulge you any further.

776
00:50:56,250 --> 00:50:57,700
你得放弃
You have to let this go.

777
00:50:58,520 --> 00:51:01,790
我可以参与你的竞选  也可以终结你的竞选
I can be a part of your campaign, or I can end it.

778
00:51:04,280 --> 00:51:07,440
我也会不惜一切  就像你父亲那样
I'll do whatever it takes, too. Just like your father.

779
00:51:08,240 --> 00:51:10,150
但我不会放弃
But I will not let this go.

780
00:51:19,610 --> 00:51:22,030
给我备辆车去格林维尔机场
I'll need a car to the Greenville Airport.

781
00:51:22,890 --> 00:51:24,950
去达拉斯  没错
To Dallas, yes.

